  "notes": "Same as q214 (detach_epos=True) but with energy_reg_weight=1e-10. At E=447k: reg_gradient=9e-5 (negligible, should not suppress pred). At E=9e13: reg_gradient=0.18 (arrests explosion). SUCCESS criteria: pred_norm\u219219.4, val MSE\u21920.0097 by step 5k-10k. FAILURE criteria: pred_norm still explodes (>100 at step 1k) OR collapses (<1 at step 10k). Abort analysis by step 5k if clearly failing.",
